name: "Hello baby" - Limited edition giclée print
description:
These original limited edition charcoal sketches capture Boofle's lovable charm and quirkiness and effectively highlight David's unique talent and imagination. The prints are signed and numbered by David and a signed certificate of authenticity will be issued with each print.

Signed and Numbered Limited edition print. Limited run of 200

SIze: 240mm x 210mm

Type: Giclée print on 310gsm Innova Paper 

Mount: Window mounted 240x210 with 190x160mm Aperture

All Prints will be sent in sleeves, recorded delivery within 3-5 days of order. (£3.00 P+P)

Next day delivery is available for an additional £3. To be eligible for next day delivery all orders must be placed by 1pm MONDAY to THURSDAY and will be delivered before 1pm the following day.

Please note, we are only offering postage to the UK within this site. If you would like us to post internationally, please contact us via the contact page for International Postage prices.

V.A.T will be charged on checkout
